=Description=

"Tara Hunt is a hot name in the blogosphere these days. From using community marketing to help Riya with its successful launch to the controversially named Pinko Marketing to her new endeavour Citizen Agency, she's at the forefront of some exciting trends and interesting ideas. 

Fortunately for me, I was able to pin her down for a few minutes to chat about her background, marketing philosophy, Citizen Agency and more."
